text: Zadębie is a village in the administrative district of Gmina Dębowa Kłoda, within Parczew County, Lublin Voivodeship, in eastern Poland. It lies approximately east of Dębowa Kłoda, east of Parczew, and north-east of the regional capital Lublin. ==References== Category:Villages in Parczew County
title: Zadębie, Parczew County
